{"word":"ἐλάσσων/ἔλασσον","slug":"ἐλάσσων/ἔλασσον","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>ἐλάσσων</el>/<el>ἔλασσον</el></b> [Attic <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἐλάττων\">ἐλάττων</a></el>; ‘smaller, less’] functions as <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ comp.\">comp.</a> of <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:μικρός\">μικρός</a></el> (<a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ q.v.\">q.v.</a>) and signifies an aspect of diminution or reduction (Attic form is used <b><a href='B:610 5:9'>1 Ti 5:9</a>; <a href='B:650 7:7'>Hb 7:7</a></b>): <b>inferior <a href='B:500 2:10'>J 2:10</a>; <a href='B:650 7:7'>Hb 7:7</a>; younger <a href='B:520 9:12'>Ro 9:12</a>.</b> As <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ adv.\">adv.</a> <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:μὴ\">μὴ</a> ἔλλατον ἐτῶν <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἑξήκοντα\">ἑξήκοντα</a></el> not less than (= under) sixty years <b><a href='B:610 5:9'>1 Ti 5:9</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:Ἐλαμίτης\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:ἐλαττονέω\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}